Observed data - both locations

library(tidyverse)
library(lubridate)
library(mgcv)  
library(plotly)
library(WRTDStidal)
library(gridExtra)
source('R/funcs.R')

##
# sf delta C3

# flow data, left moving window average of 30 days
data(sf_fldat)
fl_dat <- sf_fldat %>% 
  rename(date = Date) %>% 
  filter(station %in% 'sac') %>% 
  mutate(
    qsm = stats::filter(q, rep(1, 30)/30, sides = 1, method = 'convolution')
  )
  
# format the data to model
data(sf_dat)
sf_mod <- sf_dat %>% 
  filter(Site_Code %in% 'C3') %>% 
  rename(date = Date) %>% 
  mutate(
    doy = yday(date), 
    dec_time = decimal_date(date), 
    yr = year(date),
    yr = factor(yr),
    mo = month(date, label = T)
  ) %>% 
  left_join(fl_dat, by = 'date') %>% 
  mutate( # all variables ln-transformed
    flo = log(qsm), 
    lnchl = log(chl), 
    tss = log(tss), 
    nh = log(nh), 
    dat = 'sf'
    ) %>% 
  select(dat, date, dec_time, yr, mo, chl,lnchl, flo, nh, tss)

##
# sle

# flow data, left moving window average of 30 days
data(sl_fldat)
fl_dat <- sl_fldat %>% 
  rename(date = Date) %>% 
  mutate(
    qsm = stats::filter(q, rep(1, 30)/30, sides = 1, method = 'convolution')
  )

# format the data to model
data(sl_dat)
sl_mod <- sl_dat %>%
  rename(date = Date) %>% 
  mutate(
    doy = yday(date), 
    dec_time = decimal_date(date), 
    yr = year(date),
    yr = factor(yr),
    mo = month(date, label = T)
  ) %>% 
  left_join(fl_dat, by = 'date') %>% 
  mutate(
    flo = log(qsm),
    lnchl = log(1 + chl), 
    dat = 'sl'
    ) %>% 
  select(dat, date, dec_time, yr, mo, chl, lnchl, flo, nh, tss)

mod <- bind_rows(sf_mod, sl_mod) %>% 
  mutate(dat = factor(dat, levels = c('sf', 'sl'), labels = c('SF Delta', 'St. Lucie')))
mythm <- theme_minimal(base_family = 'serif') +
  theme(
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1), 
    axis.title.x = element_blank(), 
    # axis.title.y = element_blank(),
    panel.border = element_rect(colour = 'black', fill = NA, size = 0.5), 
    legend.position = 'top',
    legend.title = element_blank()#,
    # panel.grid.major = element_blank(), 
    # panel.grid.minor = element_blank()
  )

ylab <- expression(paste("ln-chlorophyll (", italic(mu), "g ", L^-1, ")"))

ggplot(mod, aes(x = date, y = chl, group = dat, colour = dat)) + 
  geom_line() + 
  geom_point() + 
  scale_y_log10(ylab) +
  mythm

mythm <- theme_minimal(base_family = 'serif') +
  theme(
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1), 
    axis.title.x = element_blank(), 
    # axis.title.y = element_blank(),
    panel.border = element_rect(colour = 'black', fill = NA, size = 0.5), 
    legend.position = 'top',
    legend.title = element_blank()#,
    # panel.grid.major = element_blank(), 
    # panel.grid.minor = element_blank()
  )

ylab <- expression(paste("ln-chlorophyll (", italic(mu), "g ", L^-1, ")"))

ggplot(mod, aes(x = yr, y = chl, fill = dat)) + 
  geom_boxplot() + 
  scale_y_log10(ylab) +
  mythm

mythm <- theme_minimal(base_family = 'serif') +
  theme(
    axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1), 
    axis.title.x = element_blank(), 
    # axis.title.y = element_blank(),
    panel.border = element_rect(colour = 'black', fill = NA, size = 0.5), 
    legend.position = 'top',
    legend.title = element_blank()#,
    # panel.grid.major = element_blank(), 
    # panel.grid.minor = element_blank()
  )

ylab <- expression(paste("ln-chlorophyll (", italic(mu), "g ", L^-1, ")"))

ggplot(mod, aes(x = mo, y = chl, fill = dat)) + 
  geom_boxplot() + 
  scale_y_log10(ylab) +
  mythm
